<HEAD>Bush Edges Away From Reagan on Panama</HEAD>
<NOTE>EDs: Top 6 grafs new with Fitzwater reax to Bush comments on
administration drug policy; editing thruout, no pickup</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By EVANS WITT</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Political Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
